  <li><strong>How to Play Small Connecting Cards</strong>
    <ul>
      <li>This is the hand Iâ€™m looking for when I play No-Limit Hold â€˜em. Small connecting cards (suited) - the 7c-6c, 8h-7h, 5d-4d. Thatâ€™s the kind of hand I want. Itâ€™s my favorite. And when I get it â€¦ I want my opponent to have two Aces or two Kings and to believe (as I donâ€™t) that he should play them slow. If he holds that opinion heâ€™ll give me the opportunity to get a Turn. And if I doâ€¦ I can break him</li>
